  "prompt": "How do I sign up for Quora without Facebook?",
  "response": "To sign up for Quora without using Facebook, follow these steps:\n\n1. Go to the Quora website (www.quora.com)\n\n2. Click on \"Sign Up\" at the top right corner of the page\n\n3. You'll see several sign-up options:\n- Google\n- Apple\n- Email\n\n4. Choose \"Continue with Email\" option\n\n5. Enter your email address\n\n6. Create a password\n\n7. Fill out any additional required information (like your name)\n\n8. Verify your email address by clicking the link sent to your email\n\n9. Complete your profile by adding basic information about yourself\n\nThat's it! You can now use Quora without connecting through Facebook.",
